{"tid":1666460,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩大家入黎睇下 我對琴日既睇法","createTime":"2019-10-21T03:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T17:27:00.000Z","uid":78776,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1eccc67b37c193492120b45e5e2f5b67acfd4cb5","tid":1666460,"uid":78776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:58:08.000Z","msg":"個運動由6月9到宜加，足足有4個幾月<br />\n<br />\n但係4個幾月以來，點解大家可以冇乜進步咁？<br />\n<br />\n好多前線手足被人拉，大家亂，OK！我明<br />\n<br />\n但係點解琴日又有人亂尻咁叫人跑？<br />\n<br />\n乜事都冇又跑 full gear又跑<br />\n<br />\n催淚彈未見過咩？個個齊裝都走<br />\n<br />\n叫班手足跑完之後又叫佢地翻黎，完全唔知想點<br />\n<br />\n第二，喺旺角行行下又有班手足行左去長沙灣個邊<br />\n<br />\n問佢哋點解行過去，又係唔知原因<br />\n<br />\n差唔多6點幾個陣又有人吹風去石硤尾，之後就成班一齊走<br />\n<br />\n我喺對家實笑到死，乜都唔洗做就可以令你班人自動清場<br />\n<br />\n希望大家諗下"},{"pid":"13c9c7699868c40c45d16c7fe62ece63a32bb4bf","tid":1666460,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:01:02.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2cd9f8dfa8e44e2f5951399c13e1a17671199e","tid":1666460,"uid":78776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"71ab93b6bc1ca26e24225bd7daf8a11cbcea43a0","tid":1666460,"uid":78776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:21:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5d0c225d0bfc0fb6da191813962d36b412873d18","tid":1666460,"uid":132056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:26:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天滅中共 全黨死清光</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1f4146e3a77b77ccf1ff3163684735f392470935","tid":1666460,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"如果係咁有組織你先驚呀...咁咪即係有人控制緊囉"},{"pid":"64